title: Ep 308 - Republic Day Celebration At Gokuldham
shortDesc: On the occasion of republic day, everyone in the society is asked to prepare a speech on the nation. Who would give the best speech? Will Jetha defeat Iyer? Watch to find out.

title: Ep. 308 - Suprise Performance In Independence Celebration - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldam society celebrated independence day, where the gentlemen have planned to give a speech. As Bhide was giving a monotonous speech, he was stopped before he could conclude.

title: Ep 309 - Patriotic Residents Of Gokuldham
shortDesc: On the occasion of republic day, everyone in the society is asked to prepare a speech on the nation. But, the ladies have a special surprise for the other members of the society. Watch to find out.

title: Ep 310 - Bhide Decides To Buy A Computer
shortDesc: Bhide decides to buy a computer for Sonu's better education and seeks advice from everyone. Everyone asks him to consult Jethalal in this regard and he does the same.

title: Ep 311 - Bhide On The Hunt To Buy A Computer
shortDesc: Bhide reaches Jethalal's home to discuss buying the computer. To his surprise, Jethalal already leaves for work. He proceeds to his workplace. There Jethalal makes him meet a dealer who notifies him about the brands and costs.

title: Ep 312 - Bhide Misunderstands Jethalal
shortDesc: Bhide is on his way back to the gokuldham society. On his way, he comes across an advertisement which offers a computer at a much lesser price. Bhide assumes that Jethalal is planning to grab a heavy commission from him by offering a high price.

title: Ep 313 -  Bhide Finally Places The Order With Jethalal
shortDesc: Bhide accuses Jethalal of taking commission from him. Daya on the other hand fumes in anger when she comes to know about this from Madhavi. Jethalal then, reveals the other dealer's corrupt intentions to Bhide.

title: Ep 314 - Bhides Horoscope & Computer Delivery Time Do Not Match
shortDesc: Bhide and Madhavi are very excited as their new computer is on its way. He opens the newspaper to read his horoscope when he realizes that this particular time to install the computer is not appropriate and he creates a fuss about it.

title: Ep 315 - Bhide Takes Computer Classes From Tapu
shortDesc: Bhide inaugurates his new computer in a grand way. Everyone forces him to start the system when he reveals that he doesn't know how to use the computer. Sonu suggests Tapu's name to teach Bhide how to use the computer. He readily agrees.

title: Ep 316 - Valentines Day is Round The Corner
shortDesc: Taarak beautifully gives a surprise to Anjali as a pre-valentine's day gift. She discusses that with all the other ladies of the gokuldham society.

title: Ep 317 - Gokuldham Men vs Gokuldham Women
shortDesc: Goli overhears the men of the gokuldham society speak ill about their wives. He rushes over to his mother and all the other ladies of the society and notifies them about this. They fume in anger and blast at their husbands.

title: Ep 318 - Wives Demand A Valentines Day Celebration
shortDesc: All the ladies of the Gokuldham Society are still upset with their men. When these poor fellows try to pacify their wives, their wives ask for valentine's day celebrations.

title: Ep 319 - Holy Ritual In Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: A holy ritual is organized in the Gokuldham Society for the betterment of all the relationships. Will these couples be able to solve the differences between each other?

title: Ep 320 - Love Is In The Air
shortDesc: After the holy ritual conducted in Gokuldham society, all the couples start expressing their love towards their spouses. Tapu Sena is happy seeing all the couples in so much love.

title: Ep 321 - Valentines Day Celebratrions
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham society is excited about Valentine's Day Celebration. Their excitement doubles when they see Sharman Joshi and Vatsal Seth on the stage.
